#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.148"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.148:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.148:0.2"
msgid "15. Tikaṇḍakīvagga"
msgstr "15. At Tikaṇḍakī"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.148:0.3"
msgid "148. Sappurisadānasutta"
msgstr "148. Gifts of a Good Person"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.148:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, sappurisadānāni."
msgstr "“There are these five gifts of a good person."

msgctxt "an5.148:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

#. VAR: anuggahitacitto → anaggahitacitto (bj)
msgctxt "an5.148:1.3"
msgid ""
"Saddhāya dānaṃ deti, sakkaccaṃ dānaṃ deti, kālena dānaṃ deti, "
"anuggahitacitto dānaṃ deti, attānañca parañca anupahacca dānaṃ deti."
msgstr ""
"They give a gift out of faith. They give a gift carefully. They give a gift "
"at the right time. They give a gift with no strings attached. They give a "
"gift without hurting themselves or others."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.148:2.1"
msgid ""
"Saddhāya kho pana, bhikkhave, dānaṃ datvā yattha yattha tassa dānassa vipāko "
"nibbattati, aḍḍho ca hoti mahaddhano mahābhogo, abhirūpo ca hoti dassanīyo "
"pāsādiko paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgato."
msgstr ""
"Having given a gift out of faith, in whatever place the result of that gift "
"manifests they become rich, affluent, and wealthy. And they’re attractive, "
"good-looking, lovely, of surpassing beauty."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.148:3.1"
msgid ""
"Sakkaccaṃ kho pana, bhikkhave, dānaṃ datvā yattha yattha tassa dānassa "
"vipāko nibbattati, aḍḍho ca hoti mahaddhano mahābhogo."
msgstr ""
"Having given a gift carefully, in whatever place the result of that gift "
"manifests they become rich, affluent, and wealthy."

#. VAR: kammakarāti → kammakārāti (mr)
msgctxt "an5.148:3.2"
msgid ""
"Yepissa te honti puttāti vā dārāti vā dāsāti vā pessāti vā kammakarāti vā, "
"tepi sussūsanti sotaṃ odahanti aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhapenti."
msgstr ""
"And their children, wives, bondservants, workers, and staff want to listen. "
"They pay attention and try to understand."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.148:4.1"
msgid ""
"Kālena kho pana, bhikkhave, dānaṃ datvā yattha yattha tassa dānassa vipāko "
"nibbattati, aḍḍho ca hoti mahaddhano mahābhogo;"
msgstr ""
"Having given a gift at the right time, in whatever place the result of that "
"gift manifests they become rich, affluent, and wealthy."

msgctxt "an5.148:4.2"
msgid "kālāgatā cassa atthā pacurā honti."
msgstr "And when the time is right, they get all that they need."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.148:5.1"
msgid ""
"Anuggahitacitto kho pana, bhikkhave, dānaṃ datvā yattha yattha tassa dānassa "
"vipāko nibbattati, aḍḍho ca hoti mahaddhano mahābhogo;"
msgstr ""
"Having given a gift with no strings attached, in whatever place the result "
"of that gift manifests they become rich, affluent, and wealthy."

msgctxt "an5.148:5.2"
msgid "uḷāresu ca pañcasu kāmaguṇesu bhogāya cittaṃ namati."
msgstr ""
"And their mind tends to enjoy the five refined kinds of sensual stimulation."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli3.173"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.148:6.1"
msgid ""
"Attānañca parañca anupahacca kho pana, bhikkhave, dānaṃ datvā yattha yattha "
"tassa dānassa vipāko nibbattati, aḍḍho ca hoti mahaddhano mahābhogo;"
msgstr ""
"Having given a gift without hurting themselves or others, in whatever place "
"the result of that gift manifests they become rich, affluent, and wealthy."

#. VAR: appiyato vā dāyādato → appiyadāyādato vā (bj, s1, mr) | appiyato vā dāyādato vā (s2, s3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an5.148:6.2"
msgid ""
"na cassa kutoci bhogānaṃ upaghāto āgacchati aggito vā udakato vā rājato vā "
"corato vā appiyato vā dāyādato."
msgstr ""
"And no damage comes to their property from anywhere, whether fire, flood, "
"rulers, bandits, or unloved heirs."

msgctxt "an5.148:6.3"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca sappurisadānānī”ti."
msgstr "These are the five gifts of a good person.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.148:6.4"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
